**CSS (style.css):**
```css
/* Basic Reset */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    color: white;
    background-color: #333;
}

header {
    background-color: #222;
    padding: 20px 0;
}

header nav ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    text-align: center;
}

header nav ul li {
    display: inline;
    margin: 0 20px;
}

header nav ul li a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 18px;
}

main {
    padding: 50px 10%;
}

#home {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
}

#home img {
    max-width: 200px;
    border-radius: 50%;
}

#home h1 {
    margin-top: 20px;
}

.art-piece {
    margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.art-piece img {
    width: 100%; /* Adjust based on your preference */
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

footer {
    background-color: #222;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
    header nav ul li {
        display: block;
        margin: 10px 0;
    }
}
```
